-- Court Rules Ukraine Must Pay Russian Ministry, Interfax Reports
-- B y   K a t e r y n a   C h o u r s i n a
-- 2012-09-19T13:40:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-19/court-rules-ukraine-must-pay-russian-ministry-interfax-reports.html
A Ukrainian court ruled that the
government must pay Russia 3.1 billion hryvnia ($380 million) in
compensation for the debt of gas trader United Energy Systems,
Interfax-Ukraine reported, citing the ruling.  The company failed to deliver on contracts signed with the
Russian Defense Ministry in the 1990s and guaranteed by the
government of Ukraine, according to Interfax. The company was
headed by former Prime Minister  Yulia Tymoshenko .  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kateryna Choursina in Kiev at 
 kchoursina@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
